1. *Brz* auto je neophodan u današnje vreme. (A fast car is necessary nowadays.)
2. Ona je sve vreme bila *brz* u učenju. (She was always fast in learning.)
3. *Brže* je više bolje. (Faster is better.)
4. Oni su se uvek trudili da postanu *brži*. (They always tried to become faster.)
5. Ona se bavila *brzim* sportovima. (She was involved in fast sports.)
6. Ona je bila u mogućnosti da dodje do cilja *brzo*. (She was able to reach the goal quickly.)